OL,3,CAppeal for information in 47-year-old
OL,4,Cunsolved murder case
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police is appealing for
OL,7,Finformation about the unsolved murder
OL,8,Fof taxi driver John 'Jack' Armstrong
OL,9,Fmore than 40 years ago.
OL,11,FMr Armstrong was found murdered near
OL,12,FBridgend in October 1979 after he
OL,13,Fcollected a customer from Cardiff in
OL,14,Fhis taxi.
OL,16,FHis death has been regularly reviewed
OL,17,Fby the South Wales Police Specialist
OL,18,FCrime Review Unit and detectives are
OL,19,Fcurrently investigating his death.
