OL,3,CAppeal for information in 47-year-old
OL,4,Cunsolved murder case
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Davies
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have been working on
OL,8,Freviewing this unsolved murder for
OL,9,Fseveral years and the case has been
OL,10,Fthe subject of media coverage and
OL,11,Ffeatured in a TV documentary series.
OL,13,F"Tragically, his daughter Jean, who
OL,14,Ffeatured in the TV documentary and
OL,15,Fexpressed her hope that the killer
OL,16,Fwould be found, passed away recently
OL,17,Fbefore she was able to see justice for
OL,18,Fher dad."
