OL,3,CAppeal for information in 47-year-old
OL,4,Cunsolved murder case
OL,6,FOn October 5, 1979, Jack, as he was
OL,7,Fknown by family and friends, radioed
OL,8,Fin to confirm he'd collected the fare
OL,9,Ffrom a Fairwater pub, but was not
OL,10,Fheard from again.
OL,12,FHis blood-stained taxi was found later
OL,13,Fthat evening in Treoes Lane, Treoes,
OL,14,Fnear to the Waterton Industrial Estate
OL,15,Fin Bridgend.
OL,17,FBut it wasn't until three days later
OL,18,Fthat his body was found some 11 miles
OL,19,Faway on Cowbridge Common. Mr Armstrong
OL,20,Fhad sustained catastrophic head
OL,21,Finjuries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
