OL,4,Cunsolved murder case
OL,6,FDespite extensive enquiries at the
OL,7,Ftime, which saw hundreds of statements
OL,8,Ftaken and exhibits examined, Mr
OL,9,FArmstrong's killer has never been
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FAs part of the review, exhibits have
OL,13,Fbeen re-examined and witnesses have
OL,14,Fbeen spoken to in the hope that
OL,15,Fdetectives will be able to identify
OL,16,Fand trace the killer.
OL,18,FDCI Davies added: "Despite the passage
OL,19,Fof time since Mr Armstrong's death, we
OL,20,Fremain as committed as ever to bring
OL,21,Fjustice for Jack and his family.
