OL,6,F"If the killer is still alive then
OL,7,Fthey are living with the knowledge of
OL,8,Fwhat they did for almost 47 years. I'd
OL,9,Fappeal to anyone who believes they
OL,10,Fknow the identity of the killer to do
OL,11,Fthe right thing and come forward."
OL,13,FAnyone with any information which
OL,14,Fcould assist detectives is urged to
OL,15,Fcontact the Review Unit via 101,
OL,16,Fquoting occurrence 2000304349 or by
OL,17,Fusing the Major Incident Public Portal
OL,18,F(MIPP).
